description:
This is a 32 minute workout called '30 MINUTE INTERMEDIATE CALISTHENICS WORKOUT at Home | Follow Along' from the channel Tom Peto Training.
The workout falls under Strength/Calisthenics and Strength/Body weight.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Advanced fitness levels.
The workout has a The Disciplined Grind and The Meditative Grind vibe.
The technique difficulty is Intermediate.
The effort required is Moderate and Challenging.

Original workout description: This 30 minute intermediate calisthenics workout is a follow along you can do at home! In this bodyweight strength and mobility routine you'll work your entire body with a variety of exercises designed to challenge your strength and flexibility.

Level up your bodyweight training with this fully body workout that includes pistol squats, press up progressions, and more! I will guide you through the Calisthenics exercises, providing modifications to suit your fitness level, and technique tips making it suitable for beginners and intermediates.
